ActFarm Credit Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of SHARILEE FOSSUM of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jason Skinner, whose term has expired.
